{
  "body_html": "\n\n  \n    第四节 仪表盘配置\n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \n  <link href=\"https://www.yuque.com/attachments/yuque/0/2020/css/491128/1588213910235-976bcd3a-7a9c-473d-b800-1b1df54807d4.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />\n<link href=\"https://www.yuque.com/attachments/yuque/0/2020/css/491128/1588213910286-64db0dd0-ac29-46fb-9241-76ef318b1b53.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />\n\n  \n        \n<div class=\"page\">\n    \n        <h1 class=\"book-chapter\" id=\"calibre_toc_43\">第四节 仪表盘配置</h1>\n        <div class=\"section\">\n            <h1 id=\"第四节-仪表盘配置\" class=\"calibre7\">第四节 仪表盘配置</h1>\n<h2 id=\"1、创建仪表盘\" class=\"calibre8\">1、创建仪表盘</h2>\n<h3 id=\"11、进入dashboard仪表盘页面\" class=\"calibre9\">1.1、进入Dashboard仪表盘页面</h3>\n<p class=\"calibre12\"><img alt src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/491128/1588213926244-28bdac81-4e96-448f-9aa4-306439bf7139.png\" class=\"calibre14\" /></p>\n<ul class=\"calibre17\">\n<li class=\"calibre18\">点击“Dashboard”选项，进入仪表盘页面。</li>\n<li class=\"calibre18\">点击“<img alt src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/491128/1588213926292-eb86803c-f857-4da6-a06c-0dc390c12c32.png\" class=\"calibre14\" />”按钮，用于创建仪表盘。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"2、配置仪表盘数据\" class=\"calibre13\">2、配置仪表盘数据</h2>\n<p class=\"calibre12\"><img alt src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/491128/1588213926327-e50feedc-982d-45ca-adde-40a6ef60fd9a.png\" class=\"calibre14\" />\n如上图所示，页面中列举了之前保存的图标模式（红色方框所圈的部分）。点击对应的名称，则选中该图标，对应的图标展示在页面的下方。</p>\n<h2 id=\"3、调整仪表盘的布局\" class=\"calibre13\">3、调整仪表盘的布局</h2>\n<p class=\"calibre12\">使用鼠标拖动等方法，将各图标移动到合适的位置，并调整合适的大小。\n<img alt src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/491128/1588213926381-1e0cd0fb-dc7d-4958-afc0-6aba312efd87.png\" class=\"calibre14\" /></p>\n\n        </div>\n    \n</div>\n\n        \n    \n\n\n\n",
